title: Moore's 'Where to Invade Next' acquired by new distributor
text:
> Entertainment Moore's 'Where to Invade Next' acquired by new distributor FILE- In this Sept. 10, 2015 file photo, director Michael Moore attends the "Where to Invade Next" premiere at the Toronto International Film Festival in Toronto. Moore’s latest documentary has been acquired by a newly formed distributor a not-yet-named distribution label formed by former Radius founders Tom Quinn and Jason Janego, and Alamo Drafthouse founder Tim League.
